      h4 Nesting
      p Place a <code>.btn-group</code> within another <code>.btn-group</code> when you want dropdown menus mixed with a series of buttons.

      .bd-example
        .btn-group(role='group' aria-label='Button group with nested dropdown')
          button.btn.btn-primary(type='button') 1
          button.btn.btn-primary(type='button') 2
          .btn-group(role='group')
            button.btn.btn-primary.dropdown-toggle(type='button' data-bs-toggle='dropdown' aria-expanded='false')
              | Dropdown
            ul.dropdown-menu
              li
                a.dropdown-item(href='#') Dropdown link
              li
                a.dropdown-item(href='#') Dropdown link

      pre
        code.language-html
          | &lt;div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="Button group with nested dropdown"&gt;
          |   &lt;button type='button' class="btn btn-primary"&gt;1&lt;/button&gt;
          |   &lt;button type='button' class="btn btn-primary"&gt;2&lt;/button&gt;
          |
          |   &lt;div class="btn-group" role="group"&gt;
          |     &lt;button type='button' class="btn btn-primary dropdown-toggle" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false"&gt;
          |       Dropdown
